wmsLayer.title: GA0335 Area2 2m
wmsLayer.description: This layer is a bathymetry grid of survey area two from marine survey GA0335, collected over the Petrel Sub-basin, north of the Northern Territory. A total of two areas were surveyed and gridded at two metre resolution. The colour ramp for the WMS is stretched between 45-95 metres water depth. The dataset can be downloaded at the following URL http://services.ga.gov.au/metadata-gateway/metadata/record/74866.
